#: appinfo/info.xml:12
msgid ""
"**Säker Digital Kommunikation (ITSL Hubs)**\n"
"\n"
"A secure communication platform for the Swedish public sector.\n"
"\n"
"- **Multiple channels** – SDK, Secure Email, internal messages, SMS, and FAX\n"
"- **Secure by design** – all communication handled through secure channels\n"
"- **Integration** – connects to your organization's existing systems\n"
"- **Built on Nextcloud Mail** – ITSL-customized build of the upstream Nextcloud Mail app, with SDK messaging, tagging, assignment, FAX, and audit logging for Swedish public-sector workflows"
msgstr ""
"**Säker Digital Kommunikation (ITSL Hubs)**\n"
"\n"
"A secure communication platform for the Swedish public sector.\n"
"\n"
"- **Multiple channels** – SDK, Secure Email, internal messages, SMS, and FAX\n"
"- **Secure by design** – all communication handled through secure channels\n"
"- **Integration** – connects to your organization's existing systems\n"
"- **Built on Nextcloud Mail** – ITSL-customized build of the upstream Nextcloud Mail app, with SDK messaging, tagging, assignment, FAX, and audit logging for Swedish public-sector workflows\n"

