#: lib/SetupChecks/MailTransport.php:26
msgid "Mail Transport configuration"
msgstr "Transport configuration"

#: lib/SetupChecks/MailTransport.php:43
msgid "The app.mail.transport setting is not set to smtp. This configuration can cause issues with modern email security measures such as SPF and DKIM because emails are sent directly from the web server, which is often not properly configured for this purpose. To address this, we have discontinued support for the mail transport. Please remove app.mail.transport from your configuration to use the SMTP transport and hide this message. A properly configured SMTP setup is required to ensure email delivery."
msgstr "The app.mail.transport setting is not set to smtp. This configuration can cause issues with modern email security measures such as SPF and DKIM because emails are sent directly from the web server, which is often not properly configured for this purpose. To address this, we have discontinued support for the mail transport. Please remove app.mail.transport from your configuration to use the SMTP transport and hide this message. A properly configured SMTP setup is required to ensure email delivery."

